OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FDoddie Weir's wife and son have
OL,7,Fannounced they will join World Cup
OL,8,FWinner Lewis Moody as he cycles 500
OL,9,Fmiles to fund research into motor
OL,10,Fneurone disease.
OL,12,FLate Scotland rugby legend Doddie Weir
OL,13,Fplayed for Melrose and also earned 61
OL,14,Fcaps for Scotland, representing the
OL,15,FBritish and Irish Lions on their
OL,16,Ficonic 1997 tour of South Africa,
OL,17,Fbefore being diagnosed with MND in
OL,18,F2016.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FHe launched the My Name'5 Doddie
OL,7,FFoundation in 2017, with the aim of
OL,8,Ffunding better research and treatment
OL,9,Ffor those with the condition. Since
OL,10,Fthen, the charity has contributed more
OL,11,Fthan #23.5m to research into effective
OL,12,Ftreatments and a cure for the disease.
OL,14,FLast year, Lewis Moody, the former
OL,15,FEngland captain, revealed his own MND
OL,16,Fdiagnosis and now plans to ride from
OL,17,FNewcastle to Twickenham, raising funds
OL,18,Ffor MND research with a line-up of
OL,19,Frugby greats including Jonny
OL,20,FWilkinson, Martin Johnson, Jason
OL,21,FRobinson, Phil Vickery and Tom Croft.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FDoddie Weir's wife, Kathy Weir, and
OL,7,Fson Hamish Weir, have now announced
OL,8,Fthey will join that line-up. Lewis
OL,9,FMoody said having Weir's family
OL,10,Falongside him would be "incredibly
OL,11,Fpowerful" and symbolised "carrying the
OL,12,Fbaton forward" in the fight against
OL,13,Fthe disease.
OL,15,FHe said: "Doddie did so much to change
OL,16,Fthe conversation around MND, and in
OL,17,Fmany ways this ride feels like
OL,18,Fcontinuing something he started.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@IO]sD@ZOUtD@NO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,F"Doddie inspired people because he
OL,7,Ffaced this disease head on with
OL,8,Funbelievable courage, humour and
OL,9,Fdetermination, and I think all of us
OL,10,Finvolved in the ride feel a
OL,11,Fresponsibility to keep pushing that
OL,12,Ffight forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,F"When you see Kathy and Hamish there
OL,7,Fbeside you, it's impossible not to
OL,8,Ffeel extra motivation. This ride is
OL,9,Fabout raising money, of course, but
OL,10,Fit's also about showing the MND
OL,11,Fcommunity that we're still fighting,
OL,12,Fstill driving awareness, and still
OL,13,Frefusing to accept that this disease
OL,14,Fcannot be beaten."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
