PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FThe seven-day Lewis Moody XV Ride will
OL,7,Fbegin at Newcastle Red Bulls on Sunday
OL,8,FJune 14, travelling through Ripon,
OL,9,FWorksop, Oakham, Leicester, Worcester,
OL,10,FGloucester, Bath and Bracknell, before
OL,11,Ffinishing at the Allianz Stadium,
OL,12,FTwickenham, on June 20, with the
OL,13,Friders delivering the match ball ahead
OL,14,Fof the Gallagher PREM Rugby Final.
OL,16,FLewis Moody XV Ride route:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FThe route has been designed around
OL,7,Fclubs and communities closely linked
OL,8,Fto Lewis Moody's rugby journey, but he
OL,9,Fsaid the challenge would also
OL,10,Fcelebrate the friendships forged
OL,11,Fthrough rugby.
OL,13,FHe said, "When you get diagnosed with
OL,14,Fsomething like MND, you very quickly
OL,15,Frealise how important people are. This
OL,16,Fride is about mates coming together,
OL,17,Fcommunities coming together, and
OL,18,Fhopefully showing people living with
OL,19,FMND that they are not alone.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,F"To have people like Martin, Jonny,
OL,7,FJason, Kenny and so many others riding
OL,8,Falongside me means more than I can put
OL,9,Finto words. We've shared huge moments
OL,10,Ftogether in rugby, but this feels
OL,11,Fbigger than sport."
OL,13,FAmong those riding the full route is
OL,14,FKenny Logan, a fellow MND campaigner
OL,15,Fand close friend of Doddie Weir.
OL,16,FOthers include:
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FOther former England internationals
OL,7,Fand rugby stars joining the ride
OL,8,Finclude Ben Kay, Joe Worsley, Danny
OL,9,FCare, Ben Youngs, Dan Hipkiss, Julian
OL,10,FWhite, Louis Deacon, Lee Mears and
OL,11,FAndy Gomarsall. Many of the riders
OL,12,Fplayed alongside Moody at Leicester
OL,13,FTigers, where the club enjoyed one of
OL,14,Fthe most successful periods in its
OL,15,Fhistory, while others were part of
OL,16,FEngland's 2003 Rugby World Cup-winning
OL,17,Fsquad.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,FMr Moody added: "This disease affects
OL,7,Ffamilies everywhere and we need people
OL,8,Fto rally behind the MND community in
OL,9,Fthe same way rugby people always rally
OL,10,Fbehind each other."
OL,12,FPaul Thompson, Director of Fundraising
OL,13,Fat My Name'5 Doddie Foundation, said:
OL,14,F"Lewis has already inspired so many
OL,15,Fpeople through the way he has
OL,16,Fapproached his diagnosis, and this
OL,17,Fchallenge is another example of that
OL,18,Fcourage and leadership.
OL,26,@nD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1780337465
OL,3,CDoddie Weir's wife and son join World
OL,4,CCup Winner's MND cycle
OL,6,F"This is about much more than rugby.
OL,7,FIt's about friendship, family,
OL,8,Fresilience and communities coming
OL,9,Ftogether behind a common cause. Every
OL,10,Fmile ridden and every pound raised
OL,11,Fwill help us continue accelerating
OL,12,Fresearch towards effective treatments
OL,13,Fand, ultimately, a cure for MND."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@aO]
